<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Prezentare tehnică: Sistem Irigare Automatizată Bare-Metal AVR cu interfață avansată și arhitectură Master-Slave.">
    <title>Sistem Irigare Automatizată | Bare-Metal AVR</title>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* ================= VARIABLES ================= */
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0a0a0c;
            --surface-color: #161b22;
            --border-color: #30363d;
            --text-main: #c9d1d9;
            --text-muted: #8b949e;
            --accent-green: #00ff66;
            --accent-amber: #ffb000;
            --accent-blue: #58a6ff;
            --accent-red: #ff5f56;
            
            --font-display: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
            --font-code: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            --font-body: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            
            --transition-speed: 0.3s;
        }

        /* ================= ACCESSIBILITY ================= */
        .skip-link {
            position: absolute; top: -40px; left: 0;
            background: var(--accent-green); color: var(--bg-color);
            padding: 8px 16px; z-index: 10000; font-weight: bold; font-family: var(--font-body);
            transition: top var(--transition-speed);
        }
        .skip-link:focus { top: 0; }
        :focus-visible { outline: 2px dashed var(--accent-green); outline-offset: 4px; }

        body.no-crt .scanline { display: none !important; }
        body.no-crt .glitch-hover:hover { animation: none !important; text-shadow: none !important; }
        body.no-crt .hero h1 { animation: none !important; border-right: none; }

        /* ================= SCROLLBAR ================= */
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 10px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg-color); }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--surface-color); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.2); border-color: var(--accent-green); }

        /* ================= RESET & BASE ================= */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: var(--font-body); 
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 30px 30px;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, .terminal-body, .badge, .param-value, .status, .cmd-text { 
            font-family: var(--font-display); 
            font-weight: 400; 
        }
        h1, h2 { color: var(--accent-green); }

        a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--accent-green); transition: color var(--transition-speed); }
        a:hover, a:focus { color: var(--accent-amber); }

        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; position: relative; z-index: 10; }

        /* ================= EFFECTS ================= */
        #particles-js { position: fixed; width: 100vw; height: 100vh; top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 0; }
        .scanline { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 10px; background: rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.1); opacity: 0.4; pointer-events: none; animation: scanline 8s linear infinite; z-index: 9999; }

        /* ================= TOOLTIPS ================= */
        .tech-word {
            font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 0.9em;
            position: relative; cursor: help; color: var(--accent-green);
            border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.5); transition: text-shadow var(--transition-speed);
        }
        .tech-word:hover, .tech-word:focus { text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.5); }
        .tech-word::after {
            content: attr(data-tooltip); position: absolute; bottom: 130%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #0d1117; border: 1px solid var(--accent-green); color: var(--text-main); font-family: var(--font-body);
            padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.85rem; width: max-content; max-width: 250px;
            white-space: normal; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition: opacity var(--transition-speed) ease;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.1); z-index: 100; pointer-events: none; line-height: 1.4; text-align: left;
        }
        .tech-word::before {
            content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 100%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            border-width: 6px; border-style: solid; border-color: var(--accent-green) transparent transparent transparent;
            opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition: opacity var(--transition-speed) ease; z-index: 100; pointer-events: none;
        }
        .tech-word:hover::after, .tech-word:hover::before, .tech-word:focus::after, .tech-word:focus::before { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; }

        /* ================= ANIMATIONS ================= */
        .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.5, 0, 0, 1); }
        .reveal.active { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        @keyframes blinkCursor { 50% { border-right-color: transparent; } }
        @keyframes scanline { 0% { transform: translateY(-100%); } 100% { transform: translateY(100vh); } }
        @keyframes glitch { 0% { text-shadow: 2px 0 var(--accent-amber), -2px 0 var(--accent-green); } 50% { text-shadow: -2px 0 var(--accent-amber), 2px 0 var(--accent-green); } 100% { text-shadow: 2px 0 var(--accent-amber), -2px 0 var(--accent-green); } }
        @keyframes spin { 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
        @keyframes drip { 0% { transform: translateY(-5px); opacity: 0; } 50% { opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; } }
        @keyframes dataFlow { to { background-position: 20px 0; } }

        /* ================= PUMP WIDGET ================= */
        .pump-widget {
            position: fixed; bottom: 30px; right: 30px; background: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.85);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 20px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            z-index: 1000; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition: border-color var(--transition-speed);
        }
        .pump-widget:hover { border-color: var(--accent-blue); }
        .pump-icon { width: 36px; height: 36px; border: 2px solid var(--text-muted); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; position: relative; background: #161b22; }
        .impeller { width: 18px; height: 18px; border: 2px dashed var(--accent-blue); border-radius: 50%; animation: spin 1.5s linear infinite; }
        .water-drop { width: 6px; height: 10px; background: var(--accent-blue); border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 50% / 60% 60% 40% 40%; position: absolute; bottom: -18px; animation: drip 1.2s infinite ease-in; }
        .pump-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .pump-title { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase;}
        .pump-status { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: bold; color: var(--accent-blue); font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;}
        .status-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-blue); border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent-blue); }

        /* ================= HERO & LAYOUT ================= */
        .hero { min-height: 90vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); position: relative; }
        .header-actions { position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 0; display: flex; gap: 10px; z-index: 20;}
        .terminal-header { color: var(--text-muted); font-family: var(--font-code); margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 3.8rem); margin-bottom: 20px; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.3); border-right: 3px solid var(--accent-green); white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: fit-content; animation: blinkCursor 0.8s step-end infinite; }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 750px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        
        .btn-group { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; border: 1px solid var(--accent-green); background: rgba(10, 10, 12, 0.8); color: var(--accent-green); font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 1rem; cursor: pointer; transition: all var(--transition-speed) ease; backdrop-filter: blur(4px); border-radius: 4px; }
        .btn.small { padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 0.85rem; border-color: var(--border-color); color: var(--text-muted); }
        .btn.primary { background: rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.1); font-weight: bold; }
        .btn:hover, .btn:focus { background: rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.15); border-color: var(--accent-green); color: var(--accent-green); box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.2); }
        .btn.primary:hover, .btn.primary:focus { background: var(--accent-green); color: var(--bg-color); }
        .glitch-hover:hover { animation: glitch 0.2s linear infinite; }
        
        section { padding: 80px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
        .section-title { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 25px; position: relative; display: inline-block;}
        .section-title::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -5px; left: 0; width: 50%; height: 2px; background: var(--accent-green); }
        .section-desc { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 800px; font-size: 1.05rem; }

        /* ================= ARCHITECTURE (IC DESIGN) ================= */
        .arch-container { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; background: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.5); padding: 50px 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; }
        
        .ic-node {
            flex: 1; min-width: 240px; background: #1a1a1a; border: 2px solid #333;
            border-radius: 6px; padding: 30px 20px; position: relative; text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0 2px 5px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
        .ic-node::before, .ic-node::after {
            content: ''; position: absolute; left: 10%; width: 80%; height: 8px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 6px, #888 6px, #888 12px);
        }
        .ic-node::before { top: -8px; }
        .ic-node::after { bottom: -8px; }
        
        .ic-node h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .ic-node p { font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.8; text-align: left; padding-left: 10px; }
        .ic-node p::before { content: '▪ '; color: var(--accent-green); }
        
        .connection { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; flex: 0.5; min-width: 150px; }
        .data-line {
            width: 100%; height: 3px; margin: 10px 0;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-amber) 0, var(--accent-amber) 8px, transparent 8px, transparent 16px);
            animation: dataFlow 1s linear infinite;
        }
        .connection span { font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent-amber); }

        /* ================= DRIVER SPECIFICATIONS GRID ================= */
        .specs-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .spec-card { background: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.4); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; transition: border-color var(--transition-speed); }
        .spec-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-blue); }
        .spec-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--accent-blue); margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
        .spec-card h3::before { content: '⚡'; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .spec-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

        /* ================= FLORA PROGRESS BARS ================= */
        .flora-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .flora-card { background: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.6); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-top: 3px solid var(--accent-green); border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; transition: all var(--transition-speed) ease; }
        .flora-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-green); transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.05); }
        .flora-details { padding: 25px; }
        
        .flora-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .flora-header h3 { color: var(--text-main); font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 0; }
        .badge { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 4px 8px; background: rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.1); color: var(--accent-green); border: 1px solid var(--accent-green); border-radius: 4px; }
        
        .param-group { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .param-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .param-value { color: var(--text-main); }
        
        .progress-track { width: 100%; height: 6px; background: #0d1117; border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #30363d; }
        .progress-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--accent-green); width: 0; transition: width 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.1, 0.8, 0.3, 1); }
        .reveal.active .progress-fill { width: var(--target-width); }
        
        .flora-desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); line-height: 1.5; }

        /* ================= BOM TABLE ================= */
        .table-wrapper { overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .bom-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgba(22, 27, 34, 0.85); text-align: left; }
        .bom-table th, .bom-table td { padding: 14px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
        .bom-table th { background: #0d1117; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: var(--font-body); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        
        .bom-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02); }
        .bom-table tbody tr:hover { background-color: rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.05); }
        .bom-table th:nth-child(2), .bom-table td:nth-child(2) { text-align: right; font-family: var(--font-code); color: var(--accent-amber); font-weight: bold; }
        .bom-table td:first-child { font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-main); }
        .bom-table td:last-child { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

        /* ================= ROADMAP GRID (COMPLETED STATUS) ================= */
        .roadmap-summary-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin-top: 25px; }
        .roadmap-tag { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 12px; background: rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 102, 0.2); border-radius: 4px; font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .roadmap-tag.checked { border-color: var(--accent-green); color: var(--text-main); }
        .roadmap-tag .chk-box { color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: bold; }

        /* ================= TERMINAL WINDOW & TREE ================= */
        .terminal-window { background: #0d1117; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        .terminal-bar { background: #161b22; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding: 12px 15px; display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; }
        .terminal-title { font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-left: auto; }
        .dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
        .dot.r { background: var(--accent-red); } .dot.y { background: var(--accent-amber); } .dot.g { background: #27c93f; }
        .terminal-body { padding: 20px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--text-main); }
        .prompt { color: var(--accent-green); } .comment { color: #8b949e; }
        
        .cmd-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; }
        .cmd-table th, .cmd-table td { padding: 10px 15px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
        .cmd-table th { background: #161b22; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: normal; }
        .cmd-text { color: var(--accent-amber); }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 60px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
        
        /* ================= RESPONSIVE ================= */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { animation: none; white-space: normal; border-right: none; }
            .header-actions { position: relative; top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; justify-content: flex-start; }
            .arch-container { flex-direction: column; }
            .data-line { width: 3px; height: 50px; background: repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent-amber) 0, var(--accent-amber) 8px, transparent 8px, transparent 16px); }
            
            .pump-widget { 
                bottom: 15px; right: 15px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 50%; 
                width: 50px; height: 50px; justify-content: center;
            }
            .pump-info { display: none; }
            .btn-group { flex-direction: column; width: 100%; }
            .btn { text-align: center; width: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Sari direct la conținut</a>

    <div id="particles-js" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="scanline" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <aside class="pump-widget" aria-label="Widget Status Pompă">
        <div class="pump-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="impeller"></div>
            <div class="water-drop"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pump-info">
            <span class="pump-title">Canal Irigare M1</span>
            <span class="pump-status"><span class="status-dot"></span> POMPĂ ACTIVĂ</span>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="container" id="main-content">
        <header class="hero reveal">
            <div class="header-actions">
                <button id="toggle-crt" class="btn small" aria-label="Dezactivează efectele CRT vizuale">
                    👁️‍🗨️ Toggle CRT
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-header" aria-hidden="true">victor@ubuntu:~/projects/smart-irrigation$ ./run_presentation.sh</div>
            <h1 id="typewriter" aria-label="Sistem Irigare Automatizată">Sistem_Irigare_Automatizată</h1>
            <p>
                Arhitectură Master-Slave de înaltă eficiență. Un sistem inteligent conceput pentru gestionarea automatizată a umidității plantelor la scară mică, implementat integral în C 
                <span tabindex="0" class="tech-word" role="tooltip" data-tooltip="Programare la nivel de regiștri hardware, eliminând overhead-ul librăriilor standard sau framework-urilor precum Arduino IDE.">bare-metal</span>. 
                Manipulare directă a regiștrilor AVR pentru optimizarea resurselor.
            </p>
            <div class="btn-group">
                <a href="https://github.com/razvanstefandima-11/Sistem-Automat-de-Irigare-pentru-Plante/releases/tag/1.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn primary glitch-hover">
                    ⬇️ Descărcare Software v1.0
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/razvanstefandima-11/Sistem-Automat-de-Irigare-pentru-Plante" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn glitch-hover">
                    View Source pe GitHub_
                </a>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="reveal" aria-labelledby="hw-specs">
            <h2 id="hw-specs" class="section-title">Hardware_Specs_&_BSP</h2>
            <p class="section-desc">
                Sistemul utilizează un **BSP (Board Support Package)** dedicat, mapând resursele hardware specifice pentru cele două unități de calcul ATmega328P care colaborează în timp real.
            </p>
            <div class="arch-container">
                <div class="ic-node">
                    <h3>MASTER MCU</h3>
                    <p>ATmega328P (Uno Board)</p>
                    <p>Logic Control Decizional</p>
                    <p>LCD Display (<span tabindex="0" class="tech-word" data-tooltip="Inter-Integrated Circuit - TWI.">I2C</span>)</p>
                    <p>Interfață Input Butoane</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="connection" aria-hidden="true">
                    <span>Polling Bus</span>
                    <div class="data-line"></div>
                    <span>Protocol I2C / TWI</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="ic-node">
                    <h3>SLAVE MCU</h3>
                    <p>ATmega328P (Nano Board)</p>
                    <p>Achiziție Date & Actuatori</p>
                    <p>3x Autocitiri (<span tabindex="0" class="tech-word" data-tooltip="Analog-to-Digital Converter.">ADC 10-biți</span>)</p>
                    <p>Control Pompe & Alarme</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="reveal" aria-labelledby="hal-drivers">
            <h2 id="hal-drivers" class="section-title">Hardware_Abstraction_Layer</h2>
            <p class="section-desc">
                Arhitectură software modulară, complet documentată și reutilizabilă, dezvoltată exclusiv prin control direct pe regiștri:
            </p>
            <div class="specs-grid">
                <div class="spec-card">
                    <h3>GPIO Driver</h3>
                    <p>Inițializare, gestionare pini pompe, LED-uri de stare, buzzer și achiziție digitală pentru senzorul ultrasonic.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="spec-card">
                    <h3>Interrupt Manager</h3>
                    <p>Tratarea asincronă a ecoului HC-SR04 și a pachetelor de comunicație pe magistrala I2C prin vectori ISR direct mapati.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="spec-card">
                    <h3>Timer System</h3>
                    <p>Configurare Timer0 în mod CTC pentru a genera un System Tick stabil la 1ms, esențial în algoritmul alarmei de 60 de secunde.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="spec-card">
                    <h3>EEPROM Storage</h3>
                    <p>Salvarea și citirea non-volatilă a pragurilor critice de umiditate configurate de utilizator, prevenind pierderile la panele de curent.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="spec-card">
                    <h3>ADC (10-bit)</h3>
                    <p>Conversie analog-digitală în mod blocking pentru eșantionarea precisă a celor 3 senzori capacitivi de umiditate a solului.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="spec-card">
                    <h3>I2C / TWI Driver</h3>
